OL,3,CMum's tribute to 'gorgeous angel'
OL,4,Cfollowing four-year-old's house fire
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FShe died at the scene despite the
OL,8,Fefforts of neighbours and fire crews.
OL,9,FHer mother and two-year-old sister
OL,10,Fwere taken to hospital where they
OL,11,Fremain in a stable condition.
OL,13,FIn a post on Facebook on Thursday
OL,14,Fmorning, Kiki's mother, who is in her
OL,15,F20s, said: "I miss you baby girl, fly
OL,16,Fhigh and rest easy my gorgeous angel."
OL,18,F"You didn't deserve this," she added
OL,19,Fin her story.
