OL,7,FFamily members met with officers this
OL,8,Fmorning and paid their respects at the
OL,9,Fscene, where flowers, cards and teddy
OL,10,Fbears have been left in memory of Kiki.
OL,12,FA close family member told ITV Tyne
OL,13,FTees they were "overwhelmed" with the
OL,14,Fsupport of Lynemouth and surrounding
OL,15,Fvillages.
OL,17,FReverend Julia Lacey is planning a
OL,18,Fvigil for Kiki on the village green on
OL,19,FSunday. They will gather at a tree to
OL,20,Fremember the four-year-old.
