OL,7,FPriest in charge of St Bartholemews,
OL,8,FCresswell and Lynemouth St Aidans, she
OL,9,Ftold ITV Tyne Tees: "We will say a
OL,10,Fprayer and we will come together. The
OL,11,Fcommunity have shown such tremendous
OL,12,Fsupport, but I think they also need
OL,13,Fsupport from us now."
OL,15,FThe fire service was also back on the
OL,16,Fscene on Thursday with crews seen
OL,17,Fentering the building in masks and
OL,18,Fsuits.
